author: ESPNcricinfo staff
title: Matt Henry's Kent contract cancelled due to coronavirus pandemic
description: New Zealand seamer had been due to play first seven County Championship games | ESPNcricinfo.com
content:
New Zealand seamer Matt Henry has become the latest player to have his county contract cancelled on account of the coronavirus pandemic.
Henry was due to join Kent - for whom he starred in 2018 - for seven County Championship games at the start of the season… [+1224 chars]
